description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'Low impact, beginner, fat burning, home cardio workout. ALL standing!' from the channel Body Project.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: http://teambodyproject.com 

If you'd like to take part in more workouts just like this with Daniel and the team, come and join the Team Body Project site, where we have over 400 workouts and multiple plans for all fitness levels.

Today's beginner cardio workout can be taken part at your own pace, pause whenever you have to and enjoy moving....
